snippet.title: DAVE THE DIVER: Ichiban's Holiday DLC - LAUNCH Trailer
snippet.description:
There's never a quiet day in the Blue Hole...
And it looks like Ichiban and the Bartender are caught up in another case!
Uncover a new story in "Ichiban's Holiday", out now!

※ "Ichiban's Holiday" is a limited-time DLC, available for purchase until [Oct. 9, 2025] at 07:59 AM (PDT).
※ Once purchased, the DLC will be available to play at any time.

Available on: Steam | Nintendo Switch | PlayStation 4&5
